text: IFK Holmsund is a sports club Holmsund in Sweden. It was founded on 8 June in 1923 The men's soccer team plays its home games at Kamratvallen. The club participated in the Swedish men's soccer top division in 1967. ==Notable players== *Vinnie Jones (1986) ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1923 establishments in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs
